data.description: 1/2 an acre to park your RV, boat, work equipment, or your weekend toys.  Like spending time outside?  You’re going to love the 689 sq ft screened brick paver lanai here.  It runs the entire width of the house, has an outdoor kitchen with a gas/propane stove and a full outdoor bathroom.  You’ll have plenty of room inside too because there are 3 bedrooms plus a spacious den with french doors.  The large, open kitchen overlooks the living and dining room. Perfect for entertaining.  There’s even a pantry to hide all your gadgets. This home is completely tiled throughout.  One-year-old roof and water softener system recently installed.  The beautifully landscaped backyard has tons of fruit trees (mango, coconut, guava, papaya, lemon, lime, banana) and you can bring your four-legged friends because the yard is fenced in.   Located just minutes from Lee Blvd and close to Lehigh Acres Park.  Be sure to click the 3D video for a tour!
